raw_meta_yaml:
# yaml-language-server: $schema=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/prefix-dev/recipe-format/main/schema.json
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: openlineage-sql
  version: "1.36.0"
  python_min: '3.10'

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/openlineage_sql-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d9f8f0acf0b88efa65b1af1fbd17e0ae172acca89bb5c1044794f9e313bebe82

build:
  number: 1
  script:
    - cargo-bundle-licenses --format yaml --output THIRDPARTY.yml
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - maturin >=1,<2
    - ${{ compiler("c") }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
    - ${{ compiler("rust") }}
    - cargo-bundle-licenses
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - maturin >=1,<2
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - openlineage_sql
      pip_check: true

about:
  summary: Python interface for the Rust OpenLineage lineage extraction library
  homepage: https://github.com/OpenLineage/OpenLineage
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rxm7706
    - millsks
